title: ArcGIS Managed Datastore
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors validation results for managed ArcGIS Server datastores.

 Managed datastores are internal ArcGIS-managed data stores associated with the
 Server site. Unsupported validations are treated according to the datastore
 validation rule parameters and are OK by default.
item:
 The managed datastore path.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each managed datastore validation result.
